snippet.title: Kaetram - Official Trailer (Beta)
snippet.description:
Kaetram is a 2D cross-platform pixel-based MMORPG. Play from any device and join a land of adventure filled with achievements, quests, bosses, and many areas to explore.

The game is currently in beta with many new changes coming up. We regularly update the game and use the community feedback to improve.

Website: https://kaetram.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/kaetram
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2716120/Kaetram/
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kaetram.app
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kaetram/id6468379072
Wiki: https://kaetram.wiki.gg/wiki/Kaetram_Wiki
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/kaetram
